	<name>ImEditor</name>
	<summary>Simple &amp; versatile image editor</summary>
	<description>
		<p>ImEditor is a simple image editor, supporting PNG, JPEG, WEBP, BMP, and ICO file types.</p>
		<p>It offers several tools to easily modify an image.</p>
	</description>

